# Petrovka, Novoursayevsky Selsoviet, Bakalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Petrovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Novoursayevsky Selsoviet, Bakalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 11 as of 2010.
Geography
It is located 35&nbsp;km from Bakaly and 5&nbsp;km from Novoursayevo.
